Package org.cibseven.bpm.engine.rest.security.auth

Class AuthenticationResult

java.lang.Object
org.cibseven.bpm.engine.rest.security.auth.AuthenticationResult
public class AuthenticationResult extends Object
Serves as DTO to hold the result of an authentication request performed through an AuthenticationProvider. Note that when implementing a custom AuthenticationProvider, it is not required to set groups or tenants for an AuthenticationResult, as they will be resolved later via the IdentityService (e.g. ProcessEngineAuthenticationFilter.setAuthenticatedUser(org.cibseven.bpm.engine.ProcessEngine, java.lang.String, java.util.List<java.lang.String>, java.util.List<java.lang.String>)).
